title: Kushner: Israel embassy move shows 'United States can be trusted'
text:
Kushner: Israel embassy move shows 'United States can be trusted' 3:25pm BST - 01:09
Senior White House adviser Jared Kushner says the Israel embassy move shows that when President Trump makes a promise, he keeps it and shows the world that the U.S. can be trusted.
